{"tid":1555251,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"新屋嶺同太子關我乜事？","createTime":"2019-09-09T09:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:31:16.000Z","uid":129066,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4932216a9821eb9f66f8f5d250d49645e97410e7","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:47:55.000Z","msg":"喂<br />\n係咪冇發生就會原諒popo原諒政府先？<br />\n<br />\n有發生你係咪就一定會突破曬所有道德枷鎖先？<br />\n<br />\n無論有冇發生我地對政府嘅態度都冇變架啦<br />\n警黑 警鐵合作已經成為常態<br />\n和平集會權利冇左 連出街都提心吊膽<br />\n香港已經變相戒嚴<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔追究個真相<br />\n但係<br />\n係討論區傾會有真相咩？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登有人話fc左你信唔信？[/size=4]<br />\n與其係到討論得把口 不如做啲實質嘅行動？<br />\n<br />\n大家都知<br />\n跪 絕食等等<br />\n用弱者姿態去喚醒冇良心嘅人嘅良心<br />\n係絕對冇可能嘅事<br />\n<br />\n唯一可以令更多真相浮面嘅方法<br />\n就係令強者跪低<br />\n[size=5]唔話長他人志氣 事實我哋的確係弱者<br />\n挨打嘅一方 被撚嘅一方[/size=4]<br />\n<br />\n唯一有嘅優勢<br />\n係人數 係我哋團結一致力量<br />\n各施各法 核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[size=6]去啦手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">另外想講</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">放負互屌唔緊要 覺得無力覺力自己人廢係正常<br />\n因為我地一個人的話真係好廢<br />\n蜜月期已經過左<br />\n不過 只會令我地更清楚團結一致嘅重要性<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">齊上齊落 願榮光歸香港</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n認同請分享 好人一世平安"},{"pid":"c9be9a2ed5b0100bde22be755ef0b57e074cbdbb","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f66ccc73b0964ec44a8d2281961f58d6d5e5aad","tid":1555251,"uid":317299,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"【913 八月十五】 金鐘悼義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554687</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XySvw4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXySvw4Z.jpg&h=8251e762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqGL5pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqGL5pZ.jpg&h=af6e3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94ee0835ebf4d52d5d1d61a8ec43ed103d276fa5","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:57:47.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"3334441b1c8293fcdcd4f34f4ecb80ed49fee7bc","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:57:58.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"c1130a7173831ead970a2caaeb772ee9a4fd4c5c","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"134b85b6e93962eabaebc1e6d8b5c61ad1fc524d","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"推上"},{"pid":"18bf8b125e49ac60c97394339bd49bb061ff504d","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:58:47.000Z","msg":"推去"},{"pid":"b4dda8163c4bbdfc62fb5d7975ee8b70bbc0a575","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:59:11.000Z","msg":"推車"},{"pid":"4ace4e30a2a5b6df040dc40521160ffde40e034e","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:59:22.000Z","msg":"推特"},{"pid":"0ed35641574c2ff65460cc9388e461aedf605a3e","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f26f2342acd34de58d906e2a164e59937b612931","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"04eddfcb4acf22eaab2dafbecc65620c08979d26","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:00:04.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"316b3ec119a3a79183b33b93e7a3c33e3c8c79b9","tid":1555251,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:00: